-# Home Top Image/Logo
.jumbotron.logo-image

-# Topics List
-# =============================================
.container
  .row
    .col-md-12.text-center.topic-selection-text
      .h1 Select a category
.container
  - @categories.each do |category|
    .col-md-6
      = link_to category_posts_path(category), class: "btn button btn-block event-button" do
        %span.category-button-name= category.name
